{"quote": "httpwwwlastsamuraicom Official website", "page_title": "The Last Samurai", "page_bio": "{{w|The Last Samurai}} is a 2003 in film {{w|alternate history}} film about an American army captain (OF-2) Nathan Algren who is hired to train Japan troops during the {{w|Meiji Restoration}}. In his first battle against the oppositional {{w|samurai}}, Algren is taken prisoner by Lord Katsumoto who gradually converts him to his cause. Although not historically accurate, the film covered several major issues of the {{w|Japanese history}} and was received better in Japan than in the US.", "page_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2003 in film"}